观看 Sabrina Carpenter 在 NPR 的 Tiny Desk 节目中首次亮相https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-sabrina-carpenter-make- her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-deskPoppy Burton Sat, 21 Dec 2024 11:11:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824246 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “浓缩咖啡”歌手触及了她作为“明确角质”流行歌星的声誉</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246">观看Sabrina Carpenter在NPR的小桌子上首次亮相，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>昨天（12月20日）在NPR的<em>Tiny Desk</em>系列中首次亮相 - 观看以下表演的镜头。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/espresso-sabrina-carpenter-spotify-streaming-3757741"><b>Sabrina Carpenter的“浓缩咖啡”为什么接管Spotify算法？</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>她在该系列中的工作，并带有有关明确语言的咨询警告，她看到了她最近的专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short&#39;N Sweet</a> ”的播放曲目，包括粉丝最喜欢的“ Juno”和“ Bad Chem”的演绎新的小提琴安排。</p><p>格莱美提名人以“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-and-jenna-ortega-in-horror-inspired-taste-teaser-3785996">品味</a>”开头后，对她职业生涯的开始进行了反思。她对观众说：“当我刚开始时，那是在这样的房间里。” “非常干燥的墙壁，没有像录音室中有耳机的混响一样，但是有些真实。太特别了。”</p><p>在她的整个场景中，Carpenter分享了某些歌曲的出现的故事，以及她以“明显的角质”流行歌星而闻名，这要归功于她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carptenter-scraps-custom-nonsense-outros-but-promises-surprise-cover-each-night-starting-with-abba-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-3796700">现在被退休的“废话” Outros</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="萨布丽娜·卡彭特：小桌子音乐会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BEoGvTlJMyY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她将经常的Inuendo重型移动称为“美丽，幸福的事故”时说，他们启发了她以下唱片，并在她开始写“短n&#39;sweet&#39;时给予了她“无限的感觉”。</p><p>在表演的其他地方，她分享了“ Bed Chem”的起源故事，该故事与她最好的朋友Paloma共享床后出现。当他们无意中的同时睡着并同时醒来时，她打趣道，他们的床上化学非常好。</p><p>她补充说：“所以我将其保存为标题。”然后我遇到了一个男人，我们的床化学床上非常好……她没有赚钱，所以我给了她很多荣誉。” </p><figure id="attachment_3801038" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801038" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801038" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）在麦迪逊广场花园（Madison Square Garden）举行的短暂的N&#39;Sweet Tour上演出。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801038" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）在麦迪逊广场花园（Madison Square Garden）举行的“短N&#39;Sweet”巡回演出中在舞台上演出。图片来源：克里斯托弗·波尔克（Christopher Polk）通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>最近，“ Bed Chem”被称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024"><em>NME</em>的2024年50首最佳歌曲</a>之一。瑞安·戴利（Rhian Daly）写道：“萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）使自己的性行为成为艺术 - 以至于她不得不否认自己是“世界上最角质的女孩”。</p><p> “床化学”无济于事。充满厚脸皮的歌词（“我的意思是友善”）和眨眼的委婉语，这首歌本来应该像&#39;咖啡一样无处不在。”</p><p>明年，Carpenter将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">明年将“ Short N&#39;Sweet”巡回赛带到英国</a>，明年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535">在BST Hyde Park举行了一个巨大的标题插槽</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsabrina-carpenter-tickets%2Fartist%2F2001092" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处的门票</a>。</p><p> 2025年还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a>一起看到她的标题<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera-sound-festival">Primavera Sound</a> ，并将踏上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">英国和欧洲巡回演出</a>，这将于明年与前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/rachel-chinouriri-15-01-2024-3570580"><em>NME</em>封面</a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a>一起作为特别嘉宾举行。</p><p>这些节目将于3月3日在都柏林的3arena开幕，并在伯明翰，伦敦和曼彻斯特举行了进一步的演出 - 请参阅下面的所有日期，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wr6WK%3A2K9xyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkCUhdxsCzkYRk0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>抢票。</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246">观看Sabrina Carpenter在NPR的小桌子上首次亮相，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
